title: Lease between the City and W.A.T. Dignity Corp

abstracts.abstract: BOARD BILL NO. 38  INTRODUCED BY: ALDERMAN SAMUEL MOORE    	An Ordinance authorizing Amendment No. 3 to the Amended and Restated Lease ("Amendment No. 3") between the City of St. Louis and W.A.T. Dignity Corporation, originally authorized by Ordinance 64565, which was adopted by the Board of Alderman of the City of St. Louis and approved September 28, 1998, and subsequently amended pursuant to Ordinance 64913, for property and improvements located at Whittier and Kennerly Streets.
